OL,3,CWorld Cup 2026: Scotland will face
OL,4,CHaiti first while England takes on
OL,5,CCroatia
OL,7,FFans have been monitoring the
OL,8,Fannouncements to see when and where
OL,9,Fthey can see their teams play, as ITV
OL,10,FNews Sports Editor Steve Scott reports
OL,12,FDetails of England and Scotland's
OL,13,Fgroup-stage matches at next year's
OL,14,FWorld Cup were revealed on Saturday.
OL,16,FEngland will face Croatia, Ghana and
OL,17,FPanama in group L, while Scotland will
OL,18,Fplay for a place in the knock-out
OL,19,Frounds against Brazil, Morocco and
OL,20,FHaiti in group C.
