OL,7,FSo when and where are they playing?
OL,9,FScotland's first World Cup match since
OL,10,F1998 will be on June 13, 2026 against
OL,11,FHaiti.
OL,13,FThe match will take place in Boston at
OL,14,F9pm local time.
