OL,3,CWorld Cup 2026: Scotland will face
OL,4,CHaiti first while England takes on
OL,5,CCroatia
OL,7,FScotland will then face Morocco in the
OL,8,Fsame city on June 19 at 6pm, and their
OL,9,Ffinal group-stage game will be against
OL,10,FBrazil in Miami on June 24.
OL,12,FBrazil and Scotland have faced each
OL,13,Fother four times at the World Cup `
OL,14,Fand also four of the last six times
OL,15,FScotland has qualified.
OL,17,FEngland's first match of the
OL,18,Ftournament will be on June 17 when
OL,19,Fthey will face Croatia in Dallas at
OL,20,F4pm.
