OL,7,FBefore the draw, Trump was
OL,8,Funsurprisingly presented with the
OL,9,Finaugural Fifa peace prize, which
OL,10,Frecognises individuals who have made
OL,11,F"exceptional contributions to peace
OL,12,Fand unity". The award is a hugely
OL,13,Fcontroversial one, with human rights
OL,14,Fcampaigners having urged Fifa earlier
OL,15,Fthis week not to hand the prize to
OL,16,FTrump.
